snippet.title: myhouse.wad
snippet.description:
myhouse.wad by Veddge is incredible, and deserves to be seen. This is a runthrough that gets the best ending and shows off a bit of extra stuff, but not everything. 

TURN ON SUBTITLES FOR COMMENTARY.

I don't show off what happens if you die and let it sit, and I don't show off the enormous maze in the upstairs closet that's a direct translation of the exploratory space in House of Leaves. It's rad, but also absurdly hard to navigate and there's nothing necessary for progression there, and I don't think it would be too fun to watch me get lost in it.

Also, if you turn on noclip and walk out of bounds, you get warped to the backrooms, but I didn't show that off because if you've seen one backrooms you've seen them all.
